{"tid":1590862,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[化學撚入］如何阻止狗執袋","createTime":"2019-09-24T02:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:38:21.000Z","uid":149021,"like":89,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"675e6f0f6aa813b82d99c4019c501f87ff0fb429","tid":1590862,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"經過三個月既抗爭 大家都可以發現到一樣野<br />\n班狗好鍾意捉人書包或執地下既袋<br />\n因為執地下袋 可能搵到示威者身份證明之類<br />\n如果我地將計就計又會點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yML57zxQXNE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyML57zxQXNE&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d3410734\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yML57zxQXNE</a><br />\n好似條片咁通渠水加鋁 產生氫氣壓力過大爆開 <br />\n再放鋼珠係入面 <br />\n<br />\n大家可能會話 tk自己人之類 咁如果大家退先放鋁片<br />\n之後放入袋到擺底走 咁化學反應需一段時間 狗執袋就有機會中招 <span style=\"color: red;\">可以增加狗對執袋既心理壓力 </span>唔好亂執野 <br />\n或者我地可以整定入袋做防線 狗唔敢亂推進<br />\n<br />\n或者有手足想做魔法師又冇料入手咁點？<br />\n可以試下呢個 不過注意化學反應會有熱釋出 小心熱<br />\n出煙就好扔 <br />\n<br />\n拋磚 有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41244e9981b6825bd1c5783d777872e298edd17e","tid":1590862,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:32:25.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"66db78d9f98bc2d2b3b49494276f3c53c680fa91","tid":1590862,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:32:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b4e8704ad5700f2250d404cfa063f66332d9e327","tid":1590862,"uid":149021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QiyHTkM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiyHTkM.png&h=1278eb23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsRKnd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsRKnd7.png&h=b85e74e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gptXHd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F